

# 📄 Product Requirements Document (PRD)

**Project Name:** POKY GROUP Website
**Repository:** [github.com/JospenWolongwo/poky-group](https://github.com/JospenWolongwo/poky-group)
**Tech Stack:** Next.js 14 (App Router) + Supabase + TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui + Framer Motion + i18n (next-intl)

---

## 1. 🎯 Project Goals

* Build a **professional landing site** that reflects **trust, innovation, and expertise**.
* Demonstrate **we’re not beginners** — showcase industry-standard design, smooth animations, and a modern, responsive layout.
* Support **multi-language (EN/FR) from the start** with i18n.
* Optimize for **SEO + fast performance**.
* Provide a **content hub (blog)** for visibility + thought leadership.
* Include a **contact form** that sends messages to Supabase.

---

## 2. 🖼️ Key Pages & Features

### 🌍 Landing Page (Homepage)

* Hero section (slogan + CTA button).
* Services overview with icons.
* Featured projects carousel.
* Testimonials (seed with mock data first).
* CTA → “Contact Us”.

### 🛠️ Services Page

* Cards for each service (custom software, AI-driven solutions, cloud integration, automation).
* Expandable details per service.

### 📂 Projects / Portfolio Page

* Grid of projects (image + title + description + tech stack).
* Each project links to a **detail modal/page** with:

  * Screenshots
  * Problem → Solution → Results
  * Tech stack used

### 📰 Blog

* Supabase-backed posts.
* Markdown/MDX support.
* Categories & tags.
* SEO-friendly slugs.

### 📞 Contact Page

* Form with: name, email, message.
* Sends message to Supabase → Admin notified.
* Add **reCAPTCHA** for spam protection.

### 🌓 Theme & Branding

* Dual theme:

  * Theme 1: 🔵 Blue tone from image you shared
  * Theme 2: 🟣 Purple tone
* Tailwind with custom theme config.

### 🌐 Localization (i18n)

* English (default).
* French (secondary).
* Language switcher in navbar.

### 📱 Responsiveness

* Mobile-first design.
* Optimized for all breakpoints (sm, md, lg, xl).

---

## 3. ⚙️ System Architecture

* **Frontend:** Next.js 14 (App Router)
* **UI/UX:** TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui + Framer Motion
* **Database/Auth/Storage:** Supabase
* **Images:** [Unsplash](https://unsplash.com) / [Pexels](https://pexels.com) free stock + project screenshots
* **Analytics:** Posthog or Plausible (self-hosted if needed)
* **SEO:** next-seo package
* **CI/CD:** Vercel for hosting

---

## 4. 🔑 Integrations

* **Supabase**:

  * Store blog posts
  * Contact form submissions
  * Future: user accounts + newsletter subscriptions
* **Email notifications**: Supabase Functions or Resend API
* **Image hosting**: Supabase storage buckets

---

## 5. 📊 Success Metrics

* Fast load time (Lighthouse score ≥ 90).
* Bounce rate < 40% on landing page.
* At least 1 new lead per week via contact form.
* Blog posts indexed on Google within 48h.

---

## 6. 🛠️ Developer Notes

* Use **file-based routing** in App Router.
* Keep components **atomic and reusable**.
* Write **translation-ready** strings:

  ```tsx
  t('landing.hero.title')
  ```
* Use **supabase-js client** for data ops.
* Implement dark/light theme toggle via `next-themes`.

---

## 7. 📅 Roadmap (MVP → V1)

### Phase 1 (MVP, Week 1-2)

* Landing page
* Services page
* Contact form (Supabase integration)
* i18n setup
* Theme setup

### Phase 2 (Week 3-4)

* Blog system (Supabase-backed)
* Portfolio/projects page
* Responsive design polish

### Phase 3 (Week 5-6)

* SEO optimization
* Analytics
* Deployment to Vercel
* Testing & QA
